## Limitations
The report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of the sources accessed. Some articles may not reflect the latest trends or emerging drivers of innovation. Additionally, the focus on English-language sources may exclude relevant insights from non-English publications. Further research could expand on these findings by incorporating a broader range of perspectives and more recent data.

